# .mbsyncrc

IMAPAccount iCloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
UserCmd "$(security find-generic-password -a ${USER} -s MAIL_LOGIN -w)"
PassCmd "$(security find-generic-password -a ${USER} -s MAIL_PASS -w)"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore iCloud-Remote
Account iCloud

MaildirStore Local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/INBOX

Channel iCloud
Far :iCloud-Remote:
Near :Local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent" "Drafts" "Trash"
Create Near
# Sync Pull
Sync PullNew PullGone Push
